“NINTENDO E3 2019 GAMES! First Impressions! Luigi's Mansion 3, Pokemon Sword & Shield, etc.” by 

Andre "Black Nerd"  Wooloo has...
caption:
“NINTENDO E3 2019 GAMES! First Impressions! Luigi’s Mansion 3, Pokemon Sword & Shield, etc.” by  Andre “Black Nerd”

Wooloo has a non-fluffy tail?!???  O.o?!?!??? I’ve been watching some sheep shearing after getting into Wooloo (kinda oddly satisfying), so it’s a little odd seeing the tail not fluffy like the rest of the Wooloo.  Gotta admit though, it’s actually really cute.  …It’s so tiny and lost in that fluff!  LOL  ^o^

summary: Serena: Bonny are you in here. Bonny Janet laying on a massive pile of Wooloo: Welcome to Wooloo-World, Sere. Let me get up and...
body:
Serena: Bonny are you in here.

Bonny Janet laying on a massive pile of Wooloo: Welcome to Wooloo-World, Sere. Let me get up and greet you. (Bonny does not move only stays silent for a while) There we go.

Serena: Oh my, the Wooloo have gotten to your brain

Bonny Janet: You know something? I have been thinking about how everyone in this mansion, Serena, does their job. And they do a pretty good job of it.
